params.name: depths
params.description: Depth of each stage.

params.name: hidden_sizes
params.description: Dimensionality of each stage.

params.name: downsamples
params.description: Whether or not to downsample inputs between two stages.

params.name: dim
params.description: Number of channels in Meta3D layers

params.name: key_dim
params.description: The size of the key in meta3D block.

params.name: attention_ratio
params.description: Ratio of the dimension of the query and value to the dimension of the key in MSHA block

params.name: resolution
params.description: Size of each patch

params.name: num_hidden_layers
params.description: Number of hidden layers in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: num_attention_heads
params.description: Number of attention heads for each attention layer in the 3D MetaBlock.

params.name: mlp_expansion_ratio
params.description: Ratio of size of the hidden dimensionality of an MLP to the dimensionality of its input.

params.name: hidden_dropout_prob
params.description: The dropout probability for all fully connected layers in the embeddings and encoder.

params.name: patch_size
params.description: The size (resolution) of each patch.

params.name: num_channels
params.description: The number of input channels.

params.name: pool_size
params.description: Kernel size of pooling layers.

params.name: downsample_patch_size
params.description: The size of patches in downsampling layers.

params.name: downsample_stride
params.description: The stride of convolution kernels in downsampling layers.

params.name: downsample_pad
params.description: Padding in downsampling layers.

params.name: drop_path_rate
params.description: Rate at which to increase dropout probability in DropPath.

params.name: num_meta3d_blocks
params.description: The number of 3D MetaBlocks in the last stage.

params.name: distillation
params.description: Whether to add a distillation head.

params.name: use_layer_scale
params.description: Whether to scale outputs from token mixers.

params.name: layer_scale_init_value
params.description: Factor by which outputs from token mixers are scaled.

params.name: hidden_act
params.description: The non-linear activation function (function or string) in the encoder and pooler. If string, gelu,relu, selu and gelu_new are supported.

params.name: initializer_range
params.description: The standard deviation of the truncated_normal_initializer for initializing all weight matrices.

params.name: layer_norm_eps
params.description: The epsilon used by the layer normalization layers.

params.name: image_size
params.description: The size (resolution) of each image.
